snippet.textDisplay: It is easy to support your club while winning... Now is the time to back the team up... No matter what is coming in the near future. When you recap the season..and the injuries klopp had to deal with.. It is a miracle that Liverpool stands where they are now. City had also to deal with key player injuries and it did not go that well for them.liverpool had many games where they won or tied the game in the last minutes because of great belief in themselves. But the players are human beings,so sometimes they make mistakes that costs the game. For me key fact is... gomez or lovren  not world class.lovren naot anymore  due to his age. Before his injury matip along with Virgil were world class. And further on after such a long successful period the all got a little bit sloppy what is completely normal. They will lay down this sloppiness to win the pl no doubt but I hope that will happen before they face Madrid next week. YNWA
